A 26-YEAR-OLD MAN was bust for allegedly raping a 15-year-old girl in Jacob Tshweu Street, Mohlakeng, Randfontein. Sergeant Carmen Hendricks said it happened at 8.15am on Tuesday. “The girl left school with her friend and went to the man’s place. He allegedly offered them dagga, which she refused but the friend smoked. “The complainant was offered a drink which she drank and later fell asleep.” Hendricks said when the girl woke up, she found the naked man on top of her and found she’d been raped. “A case was opened and she went to hospital. “The man will appear in court soon.